    <chapter xml:id="chapter-what-and-why">
        <title>What and Why</title>

        <section xml:id="section-intro-ds4e">
        <title>Introduction to Data Science 4 Everyone</title>
        
        <p>
            Data Science 4 Everyone is a groundbreaking initiative dedicated to making data science education accessible, equitable, and effective for all K-12 students. We believe that in today's data-driven world, every student deserves the opportunity to develop critical data literacy skills that will serve them throughout their lives.
        </p>

        <p>
            <em>Watch this introduction to learn more about our mission:</em>
            This video provides an overview of Data Science 4 Everyone's approach to making data science education accessible and engaging for all students.
        </p>

